comments: I really enjoyed Jean. She has a great sense of humor and is truly a caring teacher. She commends you if you do what is expected of you and doesn\'t take you too seriously if you don\'t. All in all, she was very fair but a bit disorganized (not entirely her fault, however.)I would take her again in the future. Super nice :)
Took her forever to grade stuff. Her tests are never on the material we study. Very disorganized nursing program they have!
